title: Spacious Corner Apartment with Fireplace - Walk to Lake Merritt
posting_body: ['Spacious Corner 1 Bedroom Unit', 'Property Address', '595 Merritt Avenue - #7 | Oakland, CA 94610', 'Available: Now', 'Offered By', 'Ivy Hill Properties', 'Description', 'Welcome to 595 Merritt', 'This unit is a large corner one bedroom apartment.', 'With its many windows you will get lots of light.', 'The unit has hardwood floors, two tone paint and period details like crown moulding.', 'The living room has a fire place and lots of windows.', 'The kitchen is large enough to have a good sized dining table.', 'There are two large walk-in closets and onsite laundry.', 'You are a short walk to Lake Merritt, Lakeshore and Grand Avenue shopping and restaurants.', 'For those that commute, there are casual carpool and trans bay stops within a short walk.', '**', 'Text Amanda at', 'show contact info', '(text only) to set up a showing or Cathy at', 'show contact info', '.', 'Masks are required to view unit**', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 1BD/1.0BA', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $2,295.00', 'Available: Now', 'Application Fee: $25.00', 'Security Deposit: $2,295.00']
